snippet.textDisplay: This is unrelated to the vid ... just came to say I'm so happy that during all this time when you could easily get money from coinbase or ftx (like many many "financial" youtubers did/do) you stick to your principles and didn't - which lbh was probably a bad decision as you can pocket the money and move on :P .. but I do appreciate your channel more and more and makes me trust you more, thanks!
